import { Input } from '../../components/Input'
import * as Styled from './styles'

export const Login = () => {
  const sendForm = e => {
    e.preventDefault()
  }

  return (
    <Styled.Login>
      <Styled.Form className='bg-dark' onSubmit={sendForm}>
        <Styled.Title>Entrar</Styled.Title>
        <Input
          className="form-control mb-3"
          type="email"
          placeholder="Digite seu email"
        />
        <Input
          className="form-control mb-3"
          type="password"
          placeholder="Digite sua senha"
        />
        <Styled.Button className="btn btn-primary">Fazer Login</Styled.Button>
      </Styled.Form>
    </Styled.Login>
  )
}
